01:07:33.420 --> 01:07:38.050 align:middle line:90%


01:07:38.050 --> 01:07:42.400 align:middle line:84%
And this point of crisis
is underlined and encircled

01:07:42.400 --> 01:07:45.073 align:middle line:84%
by this kind of growing
human awareness.

01:07:45.073 --> 01:07:48.180 align:middle line:90%


01:07:48.180 --> 01:07:50.960 align:middle line:84%
This is this
strange way in which

01:07:50.960 --> 01:07:53.450 align:middle line:90%
the world is organizing itself.

01:07:53.450 --> 01:07:56.340 align:middle line:84%
Now, it's not just
transnational.

01:07:56.340 --> 01:07:57.350 align:middle line:90%
It's transcultural.

01:07:57.350 --> 01:07:59.540 align:middle line:84%
It's almost beyond
time in some way.

01:07:59.540 --> 01:08:01.520 align:middle line:90%
Something was arising.

01:08:01.520 --> 01:08:04.370 align:middle line:84%
There's something
deeper happening here.

01:08:04.370 --> 01:08:08.240 align:middle line:84%
I feel like what we're seeing
is humanity's immune response.

01:08:08.240 --> 01:08:11.700 align:middle line:84%
There is something
happening in civilization

01:08:11.700 --> 01:08:15.830 align:middle line:84%
that was like a living system--
that we were collectively

01:08:15.830 --> 01:08:19.609 align:middle line:84%
manifesting an intelligence
