01:08:25.124 --> 01:08:28.046 align:middle line:90%
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

01:08:28.046 --> 01:08:39.750 align:middle line:90%


01:08:39.750 --> 01:08:41.450 align:middle line:90%
>> We share our DNA with trees.

01:08:41.450 --> 01:08:48.859 align:middle line:90%


