01:08:56.260 --> 01:08:59.189 align:middle line:90%


01:08:59.189 --> 01:09:01.950 align:middle line:84%
>> Whoever imagined the link
between the DNA of a tree

01:09:01.950 --> 01:09:04.229 align:middle line:90%
and ourselves?

01:09:04.229 --> 01:09:06.779 align:middle line:84%
What is nature
trying to teach us?

01:09:06.779 --> 01:09:09.660 align:middle line:10%
>> When I think about roots,
