01:09:09.660 --> 01:09:10.460 align:middle line:10%
itself--

01:09:10.460 --> 01:09:13.600 align:middle line:10%


01:09:13.600 --> 01:09:19.330 align:middle line:10%
its desire to create
seeds, to propagate.

01:09:19.330 --> 01:09:21.450 align:middle line:90%
Those seeds are the future.

01:09:21.450 --> 01:09:24.130 align:middle line:84%
And those seeds carry a little
bit of a different twist

01:09:24.130 --> 01:09:26.770 align:middle line:84%
