01:09:30.095 --> 01:09:36.378 align:middle line:90%


01:09:36.378 --> 01:09:38.170 align:middle line:84%
>> That's the wonderful
thing about nature.

01:09:38.170 --> 01:09:39.260 align:middle line:90%
It's always balanced.

01:09:39.260 --> 01:09:43.069 align:middle line:84%
There's no such
thing as imbalance.

01:09:43.069 --> 01:09:46.220 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, the biggest thing that
