01:10:00.440 --> 01:10:04.322 align:middle line:84%
And they go back into the
soil, and they feed the tree.

01:10:04.322 --> 01:10:07.226 align:middle line:90%
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

01:10:07.226 --> 01:10:15.470 align:middle line:90%


01:10:15.470 --> 01:10:17.370 align:middle line:84%
>> The idea is the
world gets better.

01:10:17.370 --> 01:10:18.170 align:middle line:90%
That is designed.

01:10:18.170 --> 01:10:21.820 align:middle line:90%


01:10:21.820 --> 01:10:24.150 align:middle line:84%
We look for a
condition of support,

01:10:24.150 --> 01:10:27.280 align:middle line:84%
