>> Nature follows the
path of least resistance.

01:11:06.150 --> 01:11:09.590 align:middle line:84%
This is the non-violent path
that Gandhi and Martin Luther

01:11:09.590 --> 01:11:12.260 align:middle line:84%
King and so many
extraordinary people

01:11:12.260 --> 01:11:16.010 align:middle line:84%
have tried to counsel us with
in terms of how we address power

01:11:16.010 --> 01:11:18.680 align:middle line:84%
and how we change
the relationship

01:11:18.680 --> 01:11:23.300 align:middle line:84%
between human beings and
concentrations of power.

01:11:23.300 --> 01:11:25.010 align:middle line:10%
>> If peace is a
state of existence,

01:11:25.010 --> 01:11:27.600 align:middle line:10%
then we certainly can get there.

01:11:27.600 --> 01:11:30.350 align:middle line:10%
All we have to do is
look at the example

01:11:30.350 --> 01:11:32.153 align:middle line:10%
