01:11:32.153 --> 01:11:33.965 align:middle line:90%
[ENERGETIC MUSIC PLAYING]

01:11:33.965 --> 01:11:35.712 align:middle line:90%


01:11:35.712 --> 01:11:37.670 align:middle line:84%
>> Natural capital was
